Package: harbouR
Title: R Client for SeaTable Collaborative Databases
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Raban", "Heller",
           email = "raban.heller@charite.de",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8006-9742"))
Description: An unofficial R client for the SeaTable REST API. Provides
    authentication with transparent base-token refresh, tidy tibble returns
    for tables, rows, columns and views, helpers for managing bases and
    files, and an optional 'shiny' explorer for interactive inspection.
    SeaTable is a trademark of SeaTable GmbH; this package is not
    affiliated with or endorsed by SeaTable GmbH.
